briefdescription.para: This class is a wrapper for a list of BillingItems and LineItems.

detaileddescription.para: This class implements the IDatabaseWrapper interface to facilitate easier database operations with the two internal lists. When any of the interface methods are called, each list is iterated and depending on the method called, the objects are inserted, updated, or deleted from the database.
The objects in each list also implement the IDatabaseWrapper class so they can also be inserted, updated, or deleted from the database easily.
